name: axios
text:
Joe Biden will face three urgent nuclear challenges upon entering the White House: 
➡️ Arms control with Russia is crumbling
➡️  Iran’s uranium stockpiles are growing
➡️ North Korea is as vexing and threatening as ever
https://t.co/yV3kQKD4GP

name: axios
text:
One ritual of becoming president-elect is the carousel of congratulatory phone calls with other world leaders.

The order in which the calls are returned is watched closely around the world.
https://t.co/q8dajQaSt3

name: axios
text:
Russia’s state-run research institute announced that its COVID-19 vaccine is 92% effective. 

Experts have criticized the lack of transparency around the vaccine and the haste with which the Kremlin approved it, but countries are lining up to gain access. https://t.co/pwcNVZx4W0
